@startuml 常规流程(Spill不触发)
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #222
  ActorBorderColor #444
  DatabaseBorderColor #666
}

participant 业务App
participant VFS
participant UlogFS
participant SparseThread
Database TmpFS
Database DiskCache
participant logtail

' 1. 业务写入日志到一级缓存
业务App -> VFS : write 写入日志块
VFS -> UlogFS: write 写入日志块
UlogFS -> TmpFS : write 写入日志块
TmpFS --> 业务App : 写入成功
note over TmpFS: 块标记 consumed = 0

' 2. logtail 增量读取(仅读 tmpfs)
logtail -> TmpFS : read 拉取日志
TmpFS --> logtail : 返回完整日志数据

' 3. logtail 上报已读区间(触发标记+投递Sparse任务)
logtail -> UlogFS : Socket上报: 已读 [0, offset]
activate UlogFS
UlogFS -> UlogFS : 同步标记块 consumed = 1
UlogFS -> SparseThread : 投递异步清理任务
deactivate UlogFS

' 4. Sparse 线程执行: 两级缓存同步打洞(彻底回收)
activate SparseThread
SparseThread -> TmpFS : punch_hole 打洞
SparseThread -> DiskCache : punch_hole 打洞
note over TmpFS,DiskCache: 两层数据全部销毁\n空间彻底释放
deactivate SparseThread

@enduml